ads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/create-1-300x228.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/create-1-768x584.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/create-1-150x114.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><\/li><li><\/li><li><\/li><li><\/li><li>You can display the sidebar by using layout builder. <a href=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/2021\/10\/26\/layout-builder-options\/\" data-type=\"URL\">Read more<\/a>.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more details from our guided video.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video controls muted poster=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2022\/01\/poster-sidebar-builder.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/sidebar-builder.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>UDesign supports some default sidebars such as shop sidebar, blog sidebar, multi-vendor plugin\u2019s store sidebar. However, if you want more sidebars, the theme allows you to register new sidebar. Please go to sidebars builder page in UDesign &gt; Sidebars menu. Please click &#8220;Add New Sidebar&#8221; button in top right area to register a new sidebar. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[10],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1862"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddab